Package org.anchoranalysis.experiment.arguments

Class OutputArguments

Object
OutputArguments
public class OutputArguments
extends Object
Arguments that can further specify an experiment's output in addition to its bean specification.

    • getOutputEnabledDelta

      public OutputEnabledDelta getOutputEnabledDelta()
      Additions/subtractions of outputs for the experiment supplied by the user.

      These are applied to an existing source of output-enabled rules (e.g. defaults from a task, or rules defined in the experiment's OutputManager.
